title: Worst Date Wednesday: His Own Pool Stick & a Restraining Order
description: Michaela went on a date with a guy who takes his pool a little to seriously.  It all started when he brought his own pool stick to the local dive bar but then he goes on to tell her his ex has a restraining order against him.... Listen to hear how it get's even worse!
